      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "## Payments Operations\nThis dashboard focuses on webhook intake quality, reconciliation failures, provider distribution, and payment-route health.\n\n### Main failure signals\n- `payment.webhook.persistence_failed`\n- `payment.reconciliation.failed`\n\n### Main technical route scope\n- `/api/v1/payments/initiate`\n- `/api/v1/payments/webhooks/credo`\n- `/api/v1/payments/webhooks/safehaven`\n- `/api/v1/payment-providers`",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.0.0",
      "title": "Operational Scope",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "Loki"
